# Standalone Website - No External Connections Required
# 
# This website operates independently without external database connections
# or third-party service dependencies.
#
# No environment variables are required for basic functionality.
# The site serves static content and does not connect to external services.

# Optional: Supabase Database Configuration
# Uncomment and configure if using Supabase features
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your-supabase-url
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key

# Optional: Sentry Error Monitoring Configuration  
# Uncomment and configure for error monitoring and alerting
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=your-sentry-dsn
# SENTRY_DSN=your-sentry-dsn
# SENTRY_ORG=your-sentry-org
# SENTRY_PROJECT=your-sentry-project
# SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=your-sentry-auth-token